issueTracker.title: Fix mobile navigation menu responsiveness
issueTracker.body: The mobile navigation menu has inconsistent spacing and doesn't properly collapse on smaller screens. The hamburger menu icon overlaps with the logo on screens smaller than 640px. Need to improve responsive design and ensure proper touch targets for mobile users.
